        <h2>Designed for the Extraordinary Home</h2>
        <p>MUNLER was born from a simple conviction: the objects you live with every day deserve to be beautiful, durable, and considered. Not trend-driven. Not disposable. Genuinely well-made.</p>
        <p>We specialise in stainless steel frames and ecological mirrors — pieces that combine industrial-grade materials with refined design sensibilities. Every product in the MUNLER range is engineered to resist the elements, maintain its clarity, and hold its shape for decades.</p>
        <p>Our mirrors use 4mm and 5mm ecological silver glass — copper-free, lead-free, distortion-free. Our stainless steel frames are 304-grade, the same alloy used in professional and marine environments. This is not compromise. This is specification.</p>
